SELECT
	a.usercode,
	a.attdate,

IF (
	day_type IS NULL,
	dutytype,

IF (day_type = 'B', '4', '5')
) AS dutytype,

IF (
	day_type IS NULL,
	absenceday,

IF (day_type = 'B', 1, 0)
) AS absenceday
FROM
	(
		SELECT
			usercode,
			DATE_sub(curdate(), INTERVAL 1 DAY) attdate,

		IF (
			WEEKDAY(
				DATE_sub(curdate(), INTERVAL 1 DAY)
			) NOT IN (5, 6),
			'4',
			'5'
		) dutytype,

	IF (
		WEEKDAY(
			DATE_sub(curdate(), INTERVAL 1 DAY)
		) NOT IN (5, 6),
		1,
		0
	) absenceday
	FROM
		`userandcard`

	AND isvalid = 'T'

select usercode,recordday,minrecord,maxrecord,
if(((minrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %08:%45:%59') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null) or (WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='X'),0,round((UNIX_TIMESTAMP(minrecord)-UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %08:%30:%00')))/60)) as latetime,
case when 
(minrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %08:%45:%59') and minrecord<=DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null)
or day_type='B')) then '1'
when minrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null)
or day_type='B') then '4' 
when minrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) and day_type is null)
or day_type='X') then '3'
when (WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) and day_type is null)
or day_type='X' then '5'
else '0' end  onduty_type,
if(maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%25:%00') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null)
or day_type='B'),round((UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%30:%00'))-UNIX_TIMESTAMP(maxrecord))/60),0)  as leaveEarlyTime,
case when maxrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %19:%00:%00') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='B') 
then concat(TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR,DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%30:%00'),maxrecord),'.',
case when TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE,DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%30:%00'),maxrecord)-TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR,DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%30:%00'),maxrecord)*60<30 
then 0 else 5 end)
when (WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='X' then concat(TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR,minrecord,maxrecord),'.',
case when TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE,minrecord,maxrecord)-TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR,minrecord,maxrecord)*60<30 then 0 else 5 end) 
else 0 end overtimeTime,
case when maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%25:%00') and maxrecord>=DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') 
and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='B') then '2'
when maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='B') then '4'
when maxrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %19:%00:%00') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='B') then '3' 
when (WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='X' then '3'
else '0' end offduty_type,
case when minrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='B') then 0.5
when maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='B') then 0.5
when maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') and minrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and ((WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) and day_type is null) or day_type='B') then 1
else 0 end absenceDay
FROM v_brushdayinfo a left join f_work_day b on a.recordday=b.WORK_DAY where recordday>=DATE_SUB(curdate(),interval 28 day)

select usercode,recordday,minrecord,maxrecord,
if(minrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %08:%45:%59') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6),0,round((UNIX_TIMESTAMP(minrecord)-UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %08:%30:%00')))/60)) as latetime,
case when minrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %08:%45:%59') and minrecord<=DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) then '1'
when minrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) then '4' 
when minrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) then '3'
when WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) then '5'
else '0' end  onduty_type,
if(maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%25:%00') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6),round((UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%30:%00'))-UNIX_TIMESTAMP(maxrecord))/60),0)  as leaveEarlyTime,
case when maxrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %19:%00:%00') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) 
then concat(TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR,DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%30:%00'),maxrecord),'.',
case when TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE,DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%30:%00'),maxrecord)-TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR,DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%30:%00'),maxrecord)*60<30 then 0
else 5 end)
when WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) then concat(TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR,minrecord,maxrecord),'.',
case when TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE,minrecord,maxrecord)-TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR,minrecord,maxrecord)*60<30 then 0
else 5 end) 
else 0 end overtimeTime,
case when maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %17:%25:%00') and maxrecord>=DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) then '2'
when maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) then '4'
when maxrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %19:%00:%00') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) then '3' 
when WEEKDAY(recordday) in (5,6) then '3'
else '0' end offduty_type,
case when minrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) then 0.5
when maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) then 0.5
when maxrecord<DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') and minrecord>DATE_FORMAT(recordday,'%Y-%m-%d %10:%30:%59') and WEEKDAY(recordday) not in (5,6) then 1
else 0 end absenceDay
FROM v_brushdayinfo where recordday>=DATE_ADD(curdate(),interval -day(curdate()) day)
